table.name: auth_group
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "name" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE)

table.name: auth_group_permissions
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: auth_permission
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_permission" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "codename" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL)

table.name: django_admin_log
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_admin_log" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "object_id" text NULL, "object_repr" varchar(200) NOT NULL, "action_flag" smallint unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("action_flag" >= 0), "change_message" text NOT NULL, "content_type_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "djangoAPI_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "action_time" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: django_content_type
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_content_type" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app_label" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "model" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

table.name: django_migrations
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_migrations" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "applied" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: django_session
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_session" ("session_key" varchar(40) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, "session_data" text NOT NULL, "expire_date" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: djangoAPI_user
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "djangoAPI_user" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "password" varchar(128) NOT NULL, "last_login" datetime NULL, "is_superuser" bool NOT NULL, "first_name" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "last_name" varchar(30) NOT NULL, "email" varchar(254) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "is_staff" bool NOT NULL, "is_active" bool NOT NULL, "date_joined" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: djangoAPI_user_groups
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "djangoAPI_user_groups" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "djangoAPI_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: djangoAPI_user_user_permissions
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "djangoAPI_user_user_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "user_id" bigint NOT NULL REFERENCES "djangoAPI_user" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: myapp_audio
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "myapp_audio" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "audioName" varchar(150) NOT NULL, "audioUrl" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "imgAudioUrl" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "author" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "historyOfAudio" varchar(350) NOT NULL)

table.name: myapp_intention
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "myapp_intention" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "intention_title" varchar(70) NOT NULL, "intention_text" varchar(350) NOT NULL, "type_of_people" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

table.name: myapp_prayer
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "myapp_prayer" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "prayer_text" varchar(200) NOT NULL)

table.name: myapp_randomimg
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "myapp_randomimg" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "img_url" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

table.name: myapp_rubriquesys
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "myapp_rubriquesys" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "rubriqueName" varchar(100) NOT NULL)
